remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c6062-113">SOAP 본문 요소에서 데이터 멤버의 위치를 지정하려면 <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 속성을 사용합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-113">Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property to specify the location of a data member in the SOAP body element.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c6062-114">이 값은 멤버의 위치를 나타내는 것이 아니라 정렬 키를 나타낼 뿐이므로 연속적일 필요가 없습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-114">The value is not required to be consecutive, because it does not represent the position of the member, only the sorting key.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c6062-115">본문 요소의 순서는 기본적으로 사전순입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-115">The order of the body elements is alphabetical by default.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c6062-116">이 속성의 의미 체계는 <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 속성의 의미 체계와 동일합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-116">The semantics of this property are the same as the semantics of the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c6062-117">다음 코드 예제에서는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 속성을 사용하여 `sourceAccount` 값, `targetAccount` 값 및 `amount` 값을 차례로 serialize합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-117">The following code example uses the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property to serialize the `sourceAccount` value first, the `targetAccount` value second and the `amount` value third.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c6062-118"><xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> 속성을 사용하지 않는 경우에는 `amount` 값이 가장 먼저 serialize됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c6062-118">If the <xref:System.ServiceModel.MessageBodyMemberAttribute.Order%2A> property is not used, the `amount` value is serialized first.</span></span>  
  
```  
[MessageContract]  
public class BankingTransaction  
{  
  [MessageHeader] public Operation operation;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=1)] public Account sourceAccount;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=2)] public Account targetAccount;  
  [MessageBodyMember(Order=3)] public int amount;  
}  
```
